The line "This film was a box office success" is inaccurate.  The article linked points out that it was the first week of release, and that it was top of the American and Chinese box office in the first week.  This isn't rare, nor is it surprising considering it was co-funded.  Overall, it's gross compared to budget wasn't too impressive, and Alt Film Guide even points out that it likely didn't even make its budget back.  (altfg.com/film/the-forbidden-kingdom-box-office/)
